        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer14067014" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17860354983919244507">I highly recommend that men DON&apos;T read this, and I highly recommend that women - particularly girls who enjoy Little Women, Jane Eyre, Sense and Sensibility, Pride and Prejudice, etc. (basically old-fashioned chick flick books with substance) - DO read this. It&apos;s sweet and funny and different, not hard to get through in a day or two, and leaves you with a good feeling. </span>
  <span id="freeText17860354983919244507" style="display:none">I highly recommend that men DON'T read this, and I highly recommend that women - particularly girls who enjoy Little Women, Jane Eyre, Sense and Sensibility, Pride and Prejudice, etc. (basically old-fashioned chick flick books with substance) - DO read this. It's sweet and funny and different, not hard to get through in a day or two, and leaves you with a good feeling. </span>
