          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Mass Market Paperback 9780140374551" href="/book/show/688906.Daddy_Long_Legs">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/42315986-hilary?shelf=houses-and-homes">houses-and-homes</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/42315986-hilary?shelf=orphan-stories">orphan-stories</a>, 
